@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

|User Query| as UQ
|Text Preprocessing| as TP
|Intent Classification| as IC
|Slot Filling| as SF
|Intent Understanding| as IU

UQ -> TP: Raw Query
TP -> IC: Processed Text
IC -> SF: Intent Type
SF -> IU: Slots + Intent
IU --> [Service Matching]

note right of IC
  Multi-intent detection
  Confidence scoring
end note

note right of SF
  NER-based slot extraction
  Context completion
end note

@enduml
